ove issues in the proper framework and to elucidate some security\nfeatures of this new approach to quantum cryptography.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2005 23:00:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 May 2006 20:58:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 12 Jul 2006 19:40:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-14"}
